    <h1 class="text-c mb-1-5 main-heading">ARK Server rules.</h1>
    <div class="card">
      <p class="mb-1-5"><strong>1. Be Kind:</strong> You must respect all users, regardless of your liking towards them. Treat others the way you want to be treated.</p>
      <p class="mb-1-5"><strong>2. No Inappropriate Language:</strong> The use of profanity should be kept to a minimum. However, any derogatory language towards any user is prohibited.</p>
      <p class="mb-1-5"><strong>3. No Bluetagging:</strong> Do not join others tribe just to grief and/or take their items.</p>
      <p class="mb-1-5"><strong>4. No Mesh Building:</strong> Do not build bases and/or stashes inside of the mesh, unattainable to others.</p>
      <p class="mb-1-5"><strong>5. No Spawn-Turrets:</strong> Do not place turrets close to spawnpoints.</p>
      <p class="mb-1-5"><strong>6. No Building On Obelisk:</strong> Do not build on and/or around obelisks.</p>
      <p class="mb-1-5"><strong>7. Build Spamming:</strong> Keep the foundationspamming to a minimum, do not randomly run around placing foundations etc.</p>
      <p class="mb-1-5"><strong>8. Passive Tames:</strong> It is unnecessary to kill passive tames.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
